player.injury_notes: Brown will miss 8 games due to multiple violations of the NFL's Personal Conduct Policy.

Bryant awaits reinstatement by the NFL after violating the terms of his contidional return.
Gordon is suspended for the fifth time, indefinitley, in violation of the NFL performance-enhancing substance and substances of abuse policies.
Williams is expected to miss 2-4 weeks.
Smith is expected to be out for 5-8 weeks following surgery.
James Jr. is out due to an offseason training injury.
Logan will miss a significant part of the season.
Perkins timetable for return is unknown.
Core was placed on Injured Reserve after suffering the injury during practice.
Latimer may not practive or attend games.
